      <item>
        <title>Blog pages show at most</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[Pablo]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Hello <a class="mention" href="https://community.frontity.org/u/josema.enzo">@josema.enzo</a></p>
<p>You can use <code>state.source.params</code> and add  <code>per_page</code>. Here’s the link to the documentation:</p>
<p><a href="https://docs.frontity.org/api-reference-1/wordpress-source#state-source-params" class="onebox" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">https://docs.frontity.org/api-reference-1/wordpress-source#state-source-params</a></p>
<p>The reading setting you mentioned doesn’t affect the REST API.</p>
<p>Let us know if get it working <img src="https://community.frontity.org/images/emoji/apple/slight_smile.png?v=9" title=":slight_smile:" class="emoji" alt=":slight_smile:"></p>
